name: StorefrontAccessToken
description: A token that's used to delegate unauthenticated access scopes to clients that need to access the unauthenticated Storefront API.

returns.name: accessScopes
returns.description: List of permissions associated with the token.

returns.name: createdAt
returns.description: The date and time when the public access token was created.

returns.name: title
returns.description: An arbitrary title for each token determined by the developer, used for reference purposes.

returns.name: updatedAt
returns.description: The date and time when the storefront access token was updated.
